            <title>[CAMEL-10966] Salesforce Maven Plugin doesn&apos;t escape strings when doing the camel-salesforce:generate phase.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-10966</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Salesforce Maven Plugin doesn&apos;t escape strings when doing the camel-salesforce:generate phase.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Enums objects (`sobject-picklist.vm`) are created without escaping characters, this results in creating invalid clases that don&apos;t compile. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
